title: DeathMetal HD v1.0.8
description:
Do you like Arkanoid or similar wall/brick/block breakout?
DeathMetal combines the best old school gameplay with cutting edge graphics and touch controls on your tablet or mobile!

FEATURES

- Fast "oldschool" action
- 40 levels (10 added in update 1.0.4)
- 4 completely different episode packs
- Online scores (can you beat the BEST score for each episode?)
- 10 power-ups (+1 life, +1 ball, magnetic paddle, increasing/decreasing paddle, ball size, speed, and the last but not the least - mighty fireball!)
- You can use touch buttons or precise tilt control to move the paddle
- Metal track "Dry Metal Guitars" by Deep Sounds
